# Supercronic crontab (parsed by the `cron` service, --profile cron).
# Format:  min hour dom month dow   command
# Timezone follows the container TZ (UTC). Output → stdout/stderr → log driver.
#
# Route format is module/controller/method. Invoke via bash (not sh) so
# cli_run.sh resolves its own path correctly.
#
# Edit to match real Manager cron routes before relying on scheduled jobs.

# Hourly health check (safe, read-only).
0 * * * *   bash /var/www/html/bin/cli_run.sh manager/health_checks

# ── Examples — uncomment and adjust to your actual routes ─────────────────────
# */5 * * * *  bash /var/www/html/bin/cli_run.sh cron/queue/process
# 0 2 * * *    bash /var/www/html/bin/cli_run.sh cron/maintenance/daily_cleanup
